{"type": "article", "id": 10714, "title": "'ANNEX' Snap Fit大理石桌", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-12T06:48:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235956M8WyfiuR9CrsDHVk.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<span>虽然大理石拥有迷人的颜色和质感，但一向给人笨重的感觉，并且易碎，所以家具也比较少使用。</span><span> </span><span>毕业于美国著名的艺术中心设计学院（ACCD）的设计师 Joe Doucet</span><span> </span><span>此次展出的系列就试图解决这样的问题，设计了可拆卸组装的大理石桌子，由</span><span>3</span><span>块手工打磨的大理石板组成，只靠重力就能将其组合</span><span>到一起，最大化地精简了结构。这套兼顾了功能性、可持续性和美感的产品也在 </span><span>Cooper-Hewitt </span><span>国家设计博物馆展出。<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235954V8Z2hOM4jaHDIBYl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71363636\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052359556fWklwnJGavCAOc7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55909091\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235955Im2kWT0hrtN4nq5Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71363636\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235955KdRO6HpzAj8EGixJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\n\n\n"}